      <div class="project-row"><div class="p-thumb"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Landbäckerei Diener"></div><div><div class="p-tag">Branding</div><div class="p-title">Landbäckerei Diener</div><div class="p-desc">Komplettes Markenkonzept: Logo, Corporate Design und Packaging für eine traditionelle Handwerksbäckerei.</div></div><div class="p-arrow">→</div></div>
      <div class="project-row"><div class="p-thumb"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Velaré Skincare"></div><div><div class="p-tag">Packaging Design</div><div class="p-title">Velaré Skincare</div><div class="p-desc">Konzeptionelles Branding und Packaging für eine fiktive Premium-Skincare-Marke.</div></div><div class="p-arrow">→</div></div>
