      <div class="project-row"><div class="p-thumb"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Surreale Bildwelten"></div><div><div class="p-tag">Photoshop Compositing</div><div class="p-title">Surreale Bildwelten</div><div class="p-desc">Bildkompositionen, die verschiedene Bildwelten zu einer neuen visuellen Geschichte zusammenfügen.</div></div><div class="p-arrow">→</div></div>
      <div class="project-row"><div class="p-thumb"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Velaro Streetwear"></div><div><div class="p-tag">Clothing & Branding</div><div class="p-title">Velaro Streetwear</div><div class="p-desc">Komplette Markenwelt: Logo, Packaging, Store-Design und Kampagnenvisuals.</div></div><div class="p-arrow">→</div></div>
      <div class="project-row"><div class="p-thumb"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Hunde Portrait"></div><div><div class="p-tag">Fotografie & Retusche</div><div class="p-title">Hunde Portrait</div><div class="p-desc">Fotografische Porträtserie mit cineastischer Bildbearbeitung und Lichtstimmung.</div></div><div class="p-arrow">→</div></div>
      <div class="project-row"><div class="p-thumb"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Athleten"></div><div><div class="p-tag">Sport Grafiken</div><div class="p-title">Athleten</div><div class="p-desc">Dynamische Sportgrafiken mit Fokus auf Komposition, Typografie und visueller Energie.</div></div><div class="p-arrow">→</div></div>
    </div>
